Why the fuck is it when Conqueror comes out and I want to play Darius and have fun in a normal draft game that some bitch ass motherfucker wants to dodge because their champ got taken? Then some chad on the other team bans Darius because no fun is allowed. Then I dodge and wait 5 minutes. I get top and lock in Darius. The enemy mid takes Kat from our mid lane and they dodge because their champ is taken. Next lobby the enemy team bans darius and I dodge and get a 15 minute timer. Why the fuck does this game fucking exist to ruin my fun. Fun Is not fucking allowed. Where the fuck is team builder. Fuck.
{{sticker:darius-angry}}

You think I don't know I'm a hypocrite I'm trying to play a game and have fun. Being literally unable to play a game and have fun because people want to have fun is funception.
